```dockerfile
FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-build
WORKDIR /app
COPY frontend/package.json frontend/package-lock.json ./
RUN npm ci --production=false
COPY frontend/ .
RUN npm run build

FROM nginx:1.25-alpine AS frontend
LABEL maintainer="team@example.com" \
      service="frontend"
RUN adduser -D -H -s /sbin/nologin appuser && \
    chown -R appuser:appuser /var/cache/nginx /var/log/nginx /etc/nginx/conf.d && \
    touch /var/run/nginx.pid && chown appuser:appuser /var/run/nginx.pid
COPY --from=frontend-build /app/dist /usr/share/nginx/html
EXPOSE 80
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
  CMD ["wget", "--no-verbose", "--tries=1", "--spider", "http://localhost:80/"]
USER appuser
CMD ["nginx", "-g", "daemon off;"]

FROM golang:1.22-alpine AS api-build
WORKDIR /app
COPY api/go.mod api/go.sum ./
RUN go mod download
COPY api/ .
RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -ldflags="-s -w" -o /server .

FROM alpine:3.19 AS api
LABEL maintainer="team@example.com" \
      service="api"
RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates && \
    adduser -D -H -s /sbin/nologin appuser
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=api-build /server .
EXPOSE 8080
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
  CMD ["wget", "--no-verbose", "--tries=1", "--spider", "http://localhost:8080/healthz"]
USER appuser
CMD ["/app/server"]

FROM python:3.11-slim AS worker-build
WORKDIR /app
COPY worker/requirements.txt .
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir --prefix=/install -r requirements.txt

FROM python:3.11-slim AS worker
LABEL maintainer="team@example.com" \
      service="worker"
RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends curl && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* && \
    useradd --no-create-home --shell /sbin/nologin appuser
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=worker-build /install /usr/local
COPY worker/ .
EXPOSE 8888
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
  CMD ["python", "-c", "import celery; exit(0)"]
USER appuser
CMD ["celery", "-A", "tasks", "worker", "--loglevel=info"]
